'''手煞車'''是在车辆停放时一种用于保持车辆安全不动的装置<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=How the Parking Brake Works {{!}} YourMechanic Advice|url=https://www.yourmechanic.com/article/how-the-parking-brake-works|accessdate=2019-05-11|work=www.yourmechanic.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309023850/https://www.yourmechanic.com/article/how-the-parking-brake-works|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在使用[[自动变速器|自动变速器]]的车辆中，手煞車也可以用于紧急停车。例如，当脚[[制动器|制动器]]因故障而完全失效时，駕駛人會使用手煞車<ref>{{Cite book|title=Car Brakes : a Guide to Upgrading, Repair and Maintenance.|last=Lawes, Jon.|date=2014|publisher=Crowood|isbn=9781847976758|location=New York|oclc=870245522}}</ref>。

